          {
            "type": "section",
            "value": {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "value": "<h2 data-block-key=\"faqov\">Overview</h2><p data-block-key=\"faqo1\">The FAQ block presents a list of questions as an accordion. Selecting a question reveals its answer; selecting it again hides it.</p><p data-block-key=\"faqo2\">It follows WAI-ARIA accordion guidance: every question is a real button inside a heading, the focus ring is clearly visible, Enter or Space toggles an answer, and the arrow keys, Home, and End move between questions.</p>",
                  "id": "c8a3f1e2-1111-0000-0000-000000000008"
                }
              ],
              "config": [
                {
                  "type": "padding_bottom",
                  "value": 1,
                  "id": "c8a3f1e2-1111-0000-0000-000000000009"
                }
              ]
            },
            "id": "c8a3f1e2-1111-0000-0000-000000000010"
          },
          {
            "type": "section",
            "value": {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "value": "<h2 data-block-key=\"faqcf\">Config</h2><p data-block-key=\"faqc1\"><b>heading_level</b>: heading level (H2–H4) used for each question, so the page keeps a sensible outline for screen-reader users. Defaults to H3.</p><p data-block-key=\"faqc2\"><b>allow_multiple</b>: when set to Yes, more than one answer can be open at once. Defaults to No, so opening one question closes the others.</p><p data-block-key=\"faqc3\"><b>accent_color</b>: hex color for the expand and collapse icon.</p><p data-block-key=\"faqc4\">Each question also takes an optional <b>ID</b>: the HTML id of the question, so linking to <b>#your-id</b> opens that question and scrolls to it.</p>",
                  "id": "c8a3f1e2-1111-0000-0000-000000000011"
                }
              ],
              "config": [
                {
                  "type": "padding",
                  "value": 1,
                  "id": "c8a3f1e2-1111-0000-0000-000000000012"
                }
              ]
            },
            "id": "c8a3f1e2-1111-0000-0000-000000000013"
          },
          {
            "type": "section",
            "value": {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "value": "<h2 data-block-key=\"faqex\">Examples</h2><h3 data-block-key=\"faqe1\">Basic FAQ (one answer open at a time)</h3>",
                  "id": "c8a3f1e2-1111-0000-0000-000000000014"
                }
              ],
              "config": [
                {
                  "type": "padding",
                  "value": 1,
